data.description: Looking to escape the city life?  Come take a look at this recently remodeled 3 bedroom/1.5 bathroom home on 5.9 acres!  The house was updated in 2020 and has gorgeous, updated finishes.  The acreage has mature trees and stunning views and would be perfect for hunting.  It is even zoned for Lewisburg Schools!  You don't want to miss this opportunity!
